data.description:
Discover your dream Palm Bay home! This 1-year-old gem offers 3 beds, 2 baths, and a bonus room/office. Hurricane-ready with metal shutters, a double garage, and a vast driveway. The backyard oasis features a fruit-filled garden and flower/vegetable beds, plus a well and septic system for self-sufficiency. Built-in pest control ensures a serene living environment.
Indulge in the luxury of a high-energy-efficient home with a screened porch and a master suite boasting a walk-in glass door shower. The guest room pampers with a soaking tub. The kitchen is a chef's delight with tall cabinets and a sizable pantry. Enjoy peace of mind as the electrical, ductwork, and plumbing are under warranty, along with a 10-year structural warranty. This home effortlessly blends elegance and functionality.
